::DrillBit::

"I think..."
He then sees the one Decepticon run at Angel Prime.
"Well he pretty much summed it up."
He right hand turns to its gattaling gun mode.
"Lets slag this Maximal rust bucket!"
He opens fire on Angel Prime.
"Stunticons, c'mon, lets fry him!"
He waited for DarkFate, Killfest, and the Stunticons to join him.
